rencyservice相关的调用链路\n   - 所有异常都集中在AdService、CartService、ProductCatalogService等组件\n\n2. **实际观察到的延迟问题与currencyservice无关**\n   - **AdService延迟最严重**：GetAds接口延迟增加3倍，出现39次异常\n   - **CartService-Redis链路问题**：Redis操作延迟增加5.3倍\n   - **ProductCatalogService也有延迟**：GetProduct延迟增加18.5%\n\n3. **错误状态码分析支持AdService问题**\n   - 状态组合显示AdService调用出现\"context deadline exceeded\"错误\n   - 大量404错误表明前端服务因下游延迟而无法正常响应\n\n4. **调用拓扑分析**\n   - 根据系统拓扑，currencyservice主要被checkoutservice调用\n   - 但当前trace数据显示的主要问题在frontend直接调用的服务（AdService、CartService等）\n\n**真正的根因分析：**\n- **主要问题**：AdService性能严重下降，导致frontend调用超时\n- **次要问题**：CartService-Redis链路延迟，影响购物车功能\n- **影响范围**：前端服务出现大量404错误，整个用户体验受到影响\n\n**建议**：需要进一步检查AdService的资源使用情况、依赖的数据库连接状态，以及Redis集群的健康状况。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n================================\n请基于上述全量信息以及你的 Trace 数据，对当前故障进行分析。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT', 'OPPOSE' 或 'NEUTRAL'。", "raw_log_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载日志数据。UUID: 53ab3ccb-326，共 2 条错误日志", "filtered_logs": "node_name,service_name,pod_name,message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6a0a987f-35d8-44aa-9f9c-9bd141e8cbb4\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to retrieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"a2473f4c-11bd-4bbc-b082-0f2a3c1f57c2\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-17T07:11:06.1524235Z\"\"}\",出现次数:3\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"e81f4448-946e-47f6-803b-657b7658bdeb\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http